& [OpeningClaim] is the safe public summary
  + [summary] is the project did not solve any open Millennium Problem, but it transformed broad source intuitions into named proof-obstruction shapes
  + [method] is source preservation, SOP decomposition, periphery inquiry, deep research when needed, admission ledgers, git-reflection walking, and model-validation scoring
  + [boundary] is every mathematical claim remains separated from proof authority unless an accepted theorem, verified proof section, or external validation source is present

& [CurrentObstructionMap] is the public-safe lane map
  + [bsd] is Birch and Swinnerton-Dyer
    = current_shape: special source-cycle corridors are meaningful, but transfer into target Mordell-Weil rank count remains unproved
    = public_lock: source_transfer_to_target_mordell_weil_rank
  + [navier_stokes] is Navier-Stokes Existence and Smoothness
    = current_shape: the quadrupole pressure-work route has local structure, but no bridge was found from tail or pressure-work control to accepted pressure smallness
    = public_lock: no_tail_budget_to_pressure_oscillation_or_L3_over_2_smallness_lemma
  + [hodge] is Hodge Conjecture
    = current_shape: correspondence and motivic frameworks organize the terrain, but no general mechanism was found that generates cycles from arbitrary rational Hodge classes
    = public_lock: no_general_correspondence_generation_from_arbitrary_hodge_class
  + [p_vs_np] is P versus NP
    = current_shape: proof complexity gives the right language, but no universal polynomial refutation or simulation theorem was identified
    = public_lock: no_universal_polynomial_refutation_or_simulation_theorem
  + [yang_mills] is Yang-Mills Existence and Mass Gap
    = current_shape: a complete construction-chain claim can be staged, but decisive estimates, regulator equivalence, OS reconstruction, and gap transfer require independent validation
    = public_lock: independent_acceptance_of_uniform_estimates_and_regulator_equivalence
  + [poincare] is Poincare Conjecture
    = current_shape: already solved externally by Perelman's Ricci-flow work; this project treats Symbolic Ricci Flow only as a non-proof diagnostic/model idea
    = public_lock: none_as_solution_lane

& [BridgeFailurePattern] is the current conceptual result
  + [pattern] is local structure often exists, but the solution-shaped bridge fails at transfer, propagation, generation, simulation, or independent validation
  + [bsd_form] is transfer failure
  + [navier_stokes_form] is propagation and accepted-criterion bridge failure
  + [hodge_form] is generation failure
  + [p_vs_np_form] is simulation or lower-bound theorem failure
  + [yang_mills_form] is validation and reconstruction-chain failure
  + [model_reading] is Symbolic Ricci Flow scoring is useful when it keeps these locks visible instead of smoothing them away

